---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Josh English — full-stack software engineer at AWS."
>
  <div class="wrapper prose about">
    <p class="eyebrow">~ cat about.md</p>
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      Josh is a full-stack software engineer with a passion for building products
      that enable significant impact for end-users. His passions include finance,
      working on motorcycles, pretending to play golf, and collecting wine.
    </p>
    <p>
      Josh's career did not start out in software engineering, but he always had a
      knack for tinkering with things. His entry into software engineering began by
      way of a bootcamp called
      <a href="https://generalassemb.ly/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">General Assembly</a>.
      He has done software engineering stints at The Desire Company (fka
      desirelist), Fitch Solutions, and is currently at Amazon Web Services. In the
      spirit of working backwards, Josh has been working on his Master's in Computer
      Science at Georgia Tech (OMSCS).
    </p>
    <p>
      Spaces that are interesting to Josh include blockchain, web3, fintech, and
      social impact.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: var(--space-xs);
  }
  .about h1 {
    margin: var(--space-2xs) 0 var(--space-m);
  }
</style>
